{"tid":2402242,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"大家知唔知冬天要食啲咩拉麵？","createTime":"2021-02-10T10:11:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-02T04:34:18.000Z","uid":21696,"like":30,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"13a5ba0f297da2e870b5638c848b906e6ffa59f7","tid":2402242,"uid":21696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T10:11:10.000Z","msg":"雖然呢排東京已經冇咁凍<br />\n但朝早起身打個冷震就決定今晚放工要食啲暖嘢<br />\n<br />\n小弟嚟日本咁耐啱啱終於食咗超過170碗拉麵<br />\n個人嚟講咁凍一係食味噌拉麵，但喉嚨有啲唔舒服，好似好燥熱咁<br />\n最後就揀食第二個候選ーー新潟嘅長岡生姜醬油拉麵<br />\n食嘅就係一間位於代代木站，叫做我武者羅嘅鋪頭<br />\n<br />\n因為緊急事態宣言緊，小弟都係仆到去，費事一到八點就收鋪<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n食嘅就係呢個特製背脂生姜醬油拉麵 &yen;1130<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f4rnRn9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff4rnRn9.jpg&h=9f7011be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n湯底一啲都唔鹹，加埋啲薑食完真係由體內暖出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n叉燒有兩種，一隻淡而稔，一隻濃而有咬口<br />\n其實另外一間喺秋葉原叫青島食堂嘅生姜我都好鍾意，咁多位巴打仲有冇其他好食嘅新潟拉麵介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果想再睇多啲拉麵望梅止渴<br />\n不妨follow一吓我instagram，交流吓啲滄海遺珠。<br />\n如果有咩問題想問都可以留言，大家一齊討論吓<br />\n<br />\n預祝大家新年快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"111997ed7a12bc707c8cdae06e8f86dbed4fec4c","tid":2402242,"uid":71433,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T10:11:56.000Z","msg":"ig？ 不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae2bbfcebb8579a862ca8577a241241c4fa097a2","tid":2402242,"uid":21696,"like":4,"dislike":16,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T10:12:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://instagram.com/ego.ramen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fego.ramen&d=9j7BdtwWq97OJFdF2FXGhQUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=5105f6ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/ego.ramen</a><br />\n<br />\n自膠唔記得貼link<br />\n希望大家會喜歡"},{"pid":"bc30e23aa2e41f2ac0d50dbafd9fac7a08f57256","tid":2402242,"uid":21696,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"111997ed7a12bc707c8cdae06e8f86dbed4fec4c","tid":2402242,"uid":71433,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T10:11:56.000Z","msg":"ig？ 不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T10:13:37.000Z","msg":"唔follow都冇所謂<br />\n最緊要不定期share吓拉麵畀大家<br />\n大家喺連登睇都夠啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae744d046663195501ea5ab1dd531be0780be26d","tid":2402242,"uid":1249,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T10:14:04.000Z","msg":"屌你老木又借連登上位"},{"pid":"8311553bd0bcd32183d19c81428e8b38bc5ee49a","tid":2402242,"uid":21696,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"ae744d046663195501ea5ab1dd531be0780be26d","tid":2402242,"uid":1249,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T10:14:04.000Z","msg":"屌你老木又借連登上位"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T10:16:17.000Z","msg":"對唔住 只係唔會個個拉麵都放上嚟<br />\n如果有興趣可以去嗰邊睇<br />\n齋睇唔follow亦得"},{"pid":"a7f4802e91c424c5853d4832d3f4bcc3685445fd","tid":2402242,"uid":154373,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T10:17:43.000Z","msg":"新木耳？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4b45cf8f7341975854bff745dd26f2aa09e1b4c","tid":2402242,"uid":63675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T10:18:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6fdfde0e4cfc1925ba089cdfc3b41356f8ec51b8","tid":2402242,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T10:19:36.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"58275fb8a22b62215c7fddad69783014ca5bdb46","tid":2402242,"uid":208553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"